    PropertyGridPanel

    public class GridPanel
extends TablePanel
    Grids are an excellent way of showing large amounts of tabular data on the client side. Essentially a supercharged table , GridPanel makes it easy to fetch, sort and filter large amounts of data. Grids are composed of two main pieces - a Store full of data and a set of columns to render.
